{"tid":2023893,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"關於CloudFlare安全問題","createTime":"2020-05-19T09:46:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T13:56:29.000Z","uid":267851,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"40e1f58066e2c9f2fb803e46c89845cd0e63a7f2","tid":2023893,"uid":267851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:46:21.000Z","msg":"我本身自己有host一啲static web page同埋自己個nextcloud。<br />\n啲website本身有ssl，但係因為想啲static page load快啲所以用左cloudfare(大概3月開始)。<br />\n由於本身個host要換ssl，換完發覺張CERT都仲係cloudflare張cert唔係我本身張cert。<br />\n然後我就感覺好似有啲問題啦，因為咁樣的話基本上cloudflare係可以睇哂中間所有資料。<br />\n我上網查都見有少量人問過呢個問題，但多數答案都係話用得cloudflare就即係trust佢，即係其實cloudflare係真係咩都睇到哂。<br />\n<br />\n咁我主要問題係，好似幾年前咪鐘庭耀做過一次網上全民投票，當時聽講cloudflare block左好多ddos，但如果資料去到cloudflare之後唔安全，我啲擔心(雖然應該都只係美國政府睇到)。<br />\n<br />\n想問下各位有咩意見?<br />\n定係付費PLAN會有啲安全啲GE SOLUTION?"},{"pid":"ca93a2270c2f47c0e4cf0d26320e305a53aa01b9","tid":2023893,"uid":228008,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:01:16.000Z","msg":"Ching 應該唔知個度做咗兩次SSL"},{"pid":"5090201befeac781573bfa37b1f83a6b739fd879","tid":2023893,"uid":267851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca93a2270c2f47c0e4cf0d26320e305a53aa01b9","tid":2023893,"uid":228008,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:01:16.000Z","msg":"Ching 應該唔知個度做咗兩次SSL"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:08:52.000Z","msg":"我意思係<br />\nuser == ssl ==&gt; cloudflare (no ssl) == ssl ==&gt; host<br />\n<br />\n但cloudflare中間decrypt左啲資料先可再connect我個host，咁中間啲username password 咪完全唔俾cloudflare睇到哂(或者third party)。"},{"pid":"e2ffdf1b7d839b3d221dcbb59a2fce0b6cd9106a","tid":2023893,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:19:18.000Z","msg":"Encryption 嗰度可以揀<br />\n你想由 cloudflare connect your server 嗰條路用<br />\n<br />\nPlain HTTP<br />\nFull HTTPS<br />\nUnchecked HTTPS (for self-signed cert)"},{"pid":"7a02d0b1cc80ef7229f0c944e97fdd771c0f5813","tid":2023893,"uid":66242,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:24:24.000Z","msg":"用得cloudflare就即係trust佢，即係其實cloudflare係真係咩都睇到哂<br />\n<br />\n唔係多數答案<br />\n呢個係標準絕對答案<br />\n無其他<br />\n<br />\n擔心信唔過就唔好經佢<br />\n<br />\n不過其實 static 嘢唔使點太擔心<br />\nDynamic 先直連 own server 都夠<br />\n視乎你個網有幾機密"},{"pid":"abb2599b6f63571cf46662558c8e4bb3f4225213","tid":2023893,"uid":73565,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:28:27.000Z","msg":"邊有得咁講 正如你用gcp aws atlas host db<br />\n你一樣可以陰謀論佢睇到你啲data"},{"pid":"fddb431f581ccaace9eb33e5a02f20316ee401e1","tid":2023893,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:35:59.000Z","msg":"用 business plan 可以去返自己張cert<br />\n或者同 cloudflare 買設張 cert 入落你部機"},{"pid":"ca8dee9021cece673a329188357f5aca04d88572","tid":2023893,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5090201befeac781573bfa37b1f83a6b739fd879","tid":2023893,"uid":267851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca93a2270c2f47c0e4cf0d26320e305a53aa01b9","tid":2023893,"uid":228008,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:01:16.000Z","msg":"Ching 應該唔知個度做咗兩次SSL"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:08:52.000Z","msg":"我意思係<br />\nuser == ssl ==&gt; cloudflare (no ssl) == ssl ==&gt; host<br />\n<br />\n但cloudflare中間decrypt左啲資料先可再connect我個host，咁中間啲username password 咪完全唔俾cloudflare睇到哂(或者third party)。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:39:21.000Z","msg":"係，多數人淨係用cloudflare做CDN<br />\nlogin果啲會直連server"},{"pid":"3f0c6d93547b5766f8825d86914a0dc2be1696bf","tid":2023893,"uid":267851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a02d0b1cc80ef7229f0c944e97fdd771c0f5813","tid":2023893,"uid":66242,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:24:24.000Z","msg":"用得cloudflare就即係trust佢，即係其實cloudflare係真係咩都睇到哂<br />\n<br />\n唔係多數答案<br />\n呢個係標準絕對答案<br />\n無其他<br />\n<br />\n擔心信唔過就唔好經佢<br />\n<br />\n不過其實 static 嘢唔使點太擔心<br />\nDynamic 先直連 own server 都夠<br />\n視乎你個網有幾機密"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:47:30.000Z","msg":"唔該哂，我都明白唔trust唔好用。佢ddos同hide real ip係好好用，但個人覺得trade off其實幾大，先問各位意見。因為中間有個personal cloud storage, 對我自己黎講幾重要，雖然事實上cloudflare唔會理，但個人感覺唔太好，所以轉走左。"},{"pid":"2ae893e6e43cec3fbfc3ba243d86af67ecfe97c9","tid":2023893,"uid":267851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abb2599b6f63571cf46662558c8e4bb3f4225213","tid":2023893,"uid":73565,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:28:27.000Z","msg":"邊有得咁講 正如你用gcp aws atlas host db<br />\n你一樣可以陰謀論佢睇到你啲data"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:52:48.000Z","msg":"謝謝，因為gcp驚都可以private 嘢tunnel去trusted zone（唔算絕對安全但感覺好少少）, 但如果佢own左我個dns， 其實我做唔到任何嘢。"},{"pid":"55d3cd7557d86d547cee7096ca7ae9c40e1f88d3","tid":2023893,"uid":267851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca8dee9021cece673a329188357f5aca04d88572","tid":2023893,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5090201befeac781573bfa37b1f83a6b739fd879","tid":2023893,"uid":267851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca93a2270c2f47c0e4cf0d26320e305a53aa01b9","tid":2023893,"uid":228008,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:01:16.000Z","msg":"Ching 應該唔知個度做咗兩次SSL"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:08:52.000Z","msg":"我意思係<br />\nuser == ssl ==&gt; cloudflare (no ssl) == ssl ==&gt; host<br />\n<br />\n但cloudflare中間decrypt左啲資料先可再connect我個host，咁中間啲username password 咪完全唔俾cloudflare睇到哂(或者third party)。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:39:21.000Z","msg":"係，多數人淨係用cloudflare做CDN<br />\nlogin果啲會直連server"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:53:36.000Z","msg":"明白，唔該晒"},{"pid":"d4ed85457d4db728000d1f2bfcb87b38be8a864c","tid":2023893,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:55:00.000Z","msg":"你用SSL咁頂層既CA都可能睇到你既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"772bb25b713771ce3625108b4739df227b9d1868","tid":2023893,"uid":116683,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":